</span><br /><span id="victor_an429" class="victor_header">Title: Transition Effects of School Grade-Level Organization on Student Achievement.
</span><br /><span id="victor_an430" class="victor_header">Author(s): Alspaugh, John W.; Harting, Roger D.
</span><br /><span id="victor_an431" class="victor_header">Source: Journal of Research and Development in Education, v28 n3 p145-49 Spr 1995
