<p><span id="victor_an447" class="victor_other">ED380245 RC019950
</span><br /><span id="victor_an448" class="victor_header">Title: An Examination of the Non-K12 School District Organizational Form in New York State.
</span><br /><span id="victor_an449" class="victor_header">Author(s): Monk, David H.
</span><br /><span id="victor_an450" class="victor_header">Pages: 52
</span><br /><span id="victor_an451" class="victor_header">Publication Date: November 1994
